    "name": "Gadget-MJM",
    "profile": "A Guyanese/Dominican born and raised in North London and now residing in a secret location known as Gadgistan. Born into both a musical family as the son of [url=https://www.discogs.com/artist/1506538-Babs-Stewart]Babs Stewart[/url] and [url=https://www.discogs.com/artist/394762-Lindel-Lewis]Lindel Lewis[/url], and raised in a community where music was always around and became Gadget's first love at a very young age. Besides dabbling with instruments and production equipment left around by his father or brother, Gadget became a young DJ/MC in the underground rave scene and was often a favourite at various showcases, party nights and radio stations. He began to get deeper into production and started building his own studio in order to take out the \"needing favours\" element, and he has never looked back since. Gadget is now a self taught Sound Engineer, Producer, Vocal Artist, Ghost Writer, DnB DJ, occasional promoter, founder and project manager of the Jazz Jousters collective and the @",
